00:45.129 --> 00:46.369
There's something about the air

00:46.380 --> 00:48.005
and just the way the sunshine is.

00:48.090 --> 00:49.090
Uh, sure, buddy. Yeah.

00:49.091 --> 00:50.758
Sure. B-brilliant. Very convincing.

00:50.843 --> 00:51.843
Wha... convincing?

00:51.844 --> 00:52.927
Oh. Responsive, too.

00:53.011 --> 00:54.303
In real time. I love it.

00:54.388 --> 00:55.972
Uhh... okay.

00:56.056 --> 00:57.256
[ robotic ] I'm going to work.

00:57.307 --> 00:58.641
Morty, good morning.

00:58.726 --> 00:59.767
Dad, good morning.

00:59.852 --> 01:01.728
I am going to work. Goodbye.

01:01.812 --> 01:03.229
What's with mom?

