02:25.062 --> 02:26.813
Morty, u-uh, come on.
There's a family emergency.

02:26.897 --> 02:27.980
Stop right there!

02:28.065 --> 02:29.190
If he leaves,
I'm giving him an "F."

02:29.274 --> 02:30.274
RICK:
He doesn't care.

02:30.317 --> 02:31.317
Aw, man!

02:31.360 --> 02:32.693
Rick, I have to go back!

02:32.778 --> 02:34.153
I think I was about
to get married!

02:34.238 --> 02:35.321
