Morty.

02:35.405 --> 02:36.239
What?!

02:36.323 --> 02:37.532
Listen to me, Morty.

02:37.616 --> 02:39.408
Get your clothes off and
get in the shower right now.

02:39.493 --> 02:41.202
Y-y-y-you got to
trust me, Morty.

02:41.286 --> 02:42.286
Ugh!

02:42.329 --> 02:43.621
