least successful con artists.

03:09.189 --> 03:11.357
You know, it's lucky for
us they're also really

03:11.441 --> 03:12.481
uncomfortable with nudity.

03:12.484 --> 03:13.651
Aw, come on, Rick.

03:13.735 --> 03:14.986
