gonna be insane today,

03:15.070 --> 03:17.113
at least let me be
insane with Jessica.

03:17.197 --> 03:18.155
I can't [burps] let
you do that, Morty.

03:18.240 --> 03:19.031
Give it to me!

03:19.116 --> 03:19.907
