03:19.992 --> 03:20.825
You give it to me!

03:20.909 --> 03:22.743
G-g-give it! No, Rick!

03:30.294 --> 03:31.460
[ aliens groaning ]

03:31.545 --> 03:33.212
Oh, God, Sir!
They're still naked!

03:33.297 --> 03:34.755
Ugh.

03:34.840 --> 03:37.091
Well, check every five Quintons
and tell me when they're not.

03:37.175 --> 03:39.385
I think we should
make Kevin look, sir.

03:39.469 --> 03:40.469
What?! No!

03:40.512 --> 03:41.929
W-w-why would you even say that?

