it with my beautiful wife.

07:49.803 --> 07:50.636
Okay.

07:50.720 --> 07:51.512
Wait... really?

07:51.596 --> 07:52.429
Yes.

07:52.514 --> 07:54.265
Yes! See you in 10 minutes!

07:54.349 --> 07:55.349
[ cellphone beeps ] Hey!

07:55.392 --> 07:56.934
I'm going to make
love to my wife!

07:57.018 --> 07:58.352
Lookin' good.

07:58.436 --> 07:59.228
Slow down!

07:59.312 --> 08:00.187
My man!

08:00.272 --> 08:01.647
[ beeping ]

08:01.731 --> 08:02.982
Aw, geez, Rick.

08:03.066 --> 08:04.733
I-I don't know if I
like this plan, you know?

08:04.818 --> 08:07.653
