t-t-t-they have a tendency

08:07.737 --> 08:08.777
to make me really nervous.

08:08.780 --> 08:09.905
Morty, relax.

08:09.990 --> 08:11.657
It's just a bunch
of 1s and 0s out there.

08:11.741 --> 08:12.950
You're gonna be fine.

08:13.034 --> 08:14.201
Just follow my lead.

08:14.286 --> 08:15.786
Yo, deejay, drop that beat.

08:15.871 --> 08:17.663
[ hip-hop beat plays ]

08:17.747 --> 08:18.581
[ cheers and applause ]

08:18.665 --> 08:20.124
Uh-oh, Morty.

08:20.208 --> 08:23.294
