one of our famous rap concerts.

08:23.378 --> 08:25.212
I don't think we can
perform our new song,

08:25.297 --> 08:27.506
"The Recipe for
Concentrated Dark Matter,"

08:27.591 --> 08:28.716
for a crowd this tiny.

08:28.800 --> 08:30.301
You got that right, Rick.

08:30.385 --> 08:33.679
[ cheers and applause ]

08:33.763 --> 08:35.431
RICK:
Now that's [burps] more like it!

08:35.515 --> 08:37.141
Morty, here we go.

08:37.225 --> 08:40.102
Let me hear everybody
say "Hey-oh!" yeah!

08:40.187 --> 08:41.520
