of your age times 10!

09:15.388 --> 09:18.557
[ beeping ]

09:18.642 --> 09:19.433
Run, Morty!

09:19.517 --> 09:20.726
Before the system reboots!

09:20.810 --> 09:22.144
[ squeaking ]

09:22.229 --> 09:23.270
JERRY:
Yeah! You like that?

09:23.355 --> 09:25.356
Now who's unremarkable?

09:25.440 --> 09:26.899
You hungry for apples?

09:26.983 --> 09:28.484
[ squeaking intensifies ]

09:28.568 --> 09:30.611
Are you hungry... for... apples?!

09:30.695 --> 09:33.322
[ squeaking stops ]

09:33.406 --> 09:34.531
[ sighs deeply ]

09:34.616 --> 09:35.616
[ chuckles ]

09:35.700 --> 09:37.243
Oh, my God.

09:37.327 --> 09:40.162
That's the best sex
I've ever had in my life.

09:40.247 --> 09:44.458
It's... it's... too good.

09:44.542 --> 09:46.752
I don't deserve this, Beth.

09:46.836 --> 09:48.921
I'm a fraud.

09:49.005 --> 09:50.005
Oh, man, Rick!

09:50.048 --> 09:51.298
W-w-w-where we running to?

09:51.383 --> 09:52.633
Out of the simulation, Morty.

09:52.717 --> 09:54.635
Normally, the chamber
operates like a treadmill,

09:54.719 --> 09:56.479
with the virtual world
disappearing behind us

09:56.554 --> 09:58.514
and being rendered in front
of us as we move through it,

09:58.598 --> 10:01.558
but while it's frozen, Morty,
we can get to...

10:01.643 --> 10:03.269
the edge.

10:03.353 --> 10:04.353
Here we go.

10:04.396 --> 10:05.271
Holy crap!

10:05.355 --> 10:06.355
Come on, Morty.

10:06.398 --> 10:07.898
[ grunts ]

10:07.983 --> 10:10.025
Sir, they're over the edge.

10:10.110 --> 10:11.193
Yes, they are.

10:11.278 --> 10:14.196
Just... as... planned.

10:14.281 --> 10:18.075
[ evil laughter ]

10:18.159 --> 10:20.077
Oh, this is going to
be such a mindfuck!

10:22.247 --> 10:24.456
Keep your eyes peeled for the
central processing room, Morty.

10:24.541 --> 10:26.208
That's how we're gonna
scam these idiots.

10:26.293 --> 10:28.627
So, hey, why do these aliens
keep coming after you, Rick,

10:28.712 --> 10:30.112
if you're so
much smarter than them?

10:30.171 --> 10:31.771
